            "id": "4579389",
            "title": "S&P 500 workforce shrinks in 2025 for first time since 2016",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\" data-end=\"254\" data-start=\"65\">Employment across S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) companies declined in 2025, marking the first annual drop in nearly a decade, according to Bank of America Global Research, with data compiled alongside Bloomberg.</p>\n<p data-end=\"405\" data-start=\"256\">Total headcount slipped to about 28.1M, ending a multi-year expansion that had steadily lifted corporate payrolls since the pandemic recovery.</p>\n<p data-end=\"697\" data-start=\"407\">The reversal suggests a shift in corporate strategy as firms prioritize efficiency, automation, and margin protection amid a slowing macro backdrop. Layoffs have been concentrated in sectors such as technology and financials, where cost discipline and restructuring efforts have intensified.</p>\n<p data-end=\"883\" data-start=\"699\">While the decline is modest relative to the broader labor market, it underscores a cooling in hiring appetite among large-cap companies that have historically driven employment growth.</p>\n<p data-end=\"883\" data-start=\"699\">Here is a chart posted by <span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Mike Zaccardi on X: </span></p>\n<p data-end=\"883\" data-start=\"699\"> </p>\n<figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span><img alt=\"Chart\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/75f04ea7cdd1537e5271f3cc1b48b700.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\" data-source=\"BofA\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"500\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 180px), 552px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/75f04ea7cdd1537e5271f3cc1b48b700.png?io=w640\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/75f04ea7cdd1537e5271f3cc1b48b700.png?io=w480 480w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/75f04ea7cdd1537e5271f3cc1b48b700.png?io=w320 320w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/75f04ea7cdd1537e5271f3cc1b48b700.png?io=w240 240w\" width=\"624\"/></span><figcaption class=\"overlay-title\"><p class=\"item-caption\"><span class=\"item-source\">BofA</span></p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
